<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>أكنبت يده.<span class="c5"> ولا يقال:</span> كنِبَتْ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
